<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Panel de Control - Alumno</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-6">Panel de Control</h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-700 mb-8">¡Bienvenido, <span class="font-semibold text-blue-600">{{username}}</span>!</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            
            <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-3">Tu Perfil</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Gestiona tu contraseña y seguridad.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/profile" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 w-full">Ver Perfil</a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-3">Materias Cursando</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Visualiza tus materias e inscríbete a nuevas.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/alumno/cursando" class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 transition duration-300 w-full">Abrir Panel</a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">Materias Aprobadas</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Revisa tu historial académico y notas finales.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/alumno/aprobadas" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-green-700 transition duration-300 w-full">Ver Rendimiento</a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-3">Inscripción a Final</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Anotate a las próximas mesas de examen final.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/alumno/finales" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-purple-700 transition duration-300 w-full">Ver Mesas</a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-6">
            <a href="/logout" class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition duration-300 text-lg shadow-sm">Cerrar Sesión</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>